### GUI Layer

#### [NEW] [main_window.py](file:///c:/Users/X1%20CARBON/Downloads/fakewriter/gui/main_window.py)

Main application window built with `customtkinter`:

- **Dark theme** with accent colors (emerald green for active, amber for paused)
- **Text Input Area**: Large text box with placeholder text, supports paste
- **Multi-Text Queue**: Ability to add multiple texts, shown as a list with drag-to-reorder
- **Settings Panel**:
  - Backspace Mode: Radio buttons (Strict / Natural / Auto-Typo)
  - End Behavior: Radio buttons (Stop / Loop / Normal)
  - Target App: Dropdown (All / Whitelist / Blacklist) + app name input
- **Control Buttons**: START (▶), PAUSE (⏸), STOP (⏹) with state-dependent styling
- **Hotkey Display**: Shows configured hotkeys
- **Status Bar**: Shows Active/Paused/Done + character progress

#### [NEW] [floating_widget.py](file:///c:/Users/X1%20CARBON/Downloads/fakewriter/gui/floating_widget.py)

Transparent always-on-top overlay widget:

- Small pill-shaped widget in the top-right corner
- Shows: Status indicator (colored dot), progress `[32/150]`, next few chars preview
- Draggable by the user
- Semi-transparent background
- Auto-hides when FakeWriter is inactive

